  <script type="text/javascript">
   $(function() {
    $.fn.scrollToTop = function() {
    $(this).hide().removeAttr("href");
    if ($(window).scrollTop() != "0") {
        $(this).fadeIn("slow")
    }
    var scrollDiv = $(this);
    $(window).scroll(function() {
        if ($(window).scrollTop() == "0") {
        $(scrollDiv).fadeOut("slow")
        } else {
        $(scrollDiv).fadeIn("slow")
        }
    });
    $(this).click(function() {
        $("html, body").animate({
        scrollTop: 0
        }, "slow")
    })
    }
});
$(function() {
    $("#MD-StoTop").scrollToTop();
});

            <h1 class="post-title entry-title" itemprop="name">
             Aiza Seguerra and Liza Dio's pre-wedding photos
            </h1>
            <div class="title-secondary">
             Tuesday, December 02, 2014 - Posted by:
             <a>
              Jose Nies
             </a>
             <span class="comment-sec">
              <span class="comment-t">
              </span>
              <a href="http://www.trendingscoopnow.com/2014/12/aiza-seguerra-and-liza-dinos-pre.html#comment-form" onclick="">
               0
              </a>
             </span>
            </div>
            <div class="post-header-line-1">
            </div>
            <div class="post-body entry-content" id="post-body-7329248141790034895">
             <p>
             </p>
             <div style="text-align: justify;">
              Acoustic singer
              <b>
               Aiza Seguerra
              </b>
              and actress
              <b>
               Liza Dio
              </b>
              prenuptial photos were finally released online via Lizas Instagram account. The photos show how the lovers enjoyed and loved each other unconditionally. Check out some of their prenup pictures below:
             </div>
             <div style="text-align: justify;">
              <br/>
             </div>
             <blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned="" data-instgrm-version="4" style="background: #FFF; border-radius: 3px; border: 0; box-shadow: 0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width: 658px; padding: 0; width: -webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width: 99.375%; width: calc(100% - 2px);">
              <div style="padding: 8px;">
               <div style="background: #F8F8F8; line-height: 0; margin-top: 40px; padding: 50% 0; text-align: center; width: 100%;">
                <div style="background: url(data:image/png; display: block; height: 44px; margin: 0 auto -44px; position: relative; top: -22px; width: 44px;">
                </div>
               </div>
               <div style="margin: 8px 0 0 0; padding: 0 4px;">
                <a href="https://instagram.com/p/v65i79wTRI/" style="color: black; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 17px; text-decoration: none; word-wrap: break-word;" target="_top">
                 #Zazaroadto4ever @pjpangilinan1 @theproudrad @cyseguerra @lizadino @aavellana @jasonmagbanua
                </a>
               </div>
               <div style="color: #c9c8cd; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px; margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 8px; overflow: hidden; padding: 8px 0 7px; text-align: center; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap;">
                A photo posted by ProudRad (@theproudrad) on
                <time datetime="2014-11-27T22:41:20+00:00" style="font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px;">
                 Nov 11, 2014 at 2:41pm PST
                </time>
               </div>
              </div>
             </blockquote>
             <script async="" defer="" src="//platform.instagram.com/en_US/embeds.js">
             </script>
             <div style="text-align: justify;">
              <div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">
               <a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-mfiSpcvWIE4/VH2mYesr3fI/AAAAAAAAA8E/tAI3uQuFFCc/s1600/Aiza%2BSeguerra%2Band%2BLiza%2BDi%C3%B1o%2Bprenup%2Bphotos1.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;">
                <img border="0" height="280" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-mfiSpcvWIE4/VH2mYesr3fI/AAAAAAAAA8E/tAI3uQuFFCc/s1600/Aiza%2BSeguerra%2Band%2BLiza%2BDi%C3%B1o%2Bprenup%2Bphotos1.jpg" width="320"/>
               </a>
              </div>
              <br/>
              <div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">
               <a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-8j3zPHYgwYM/VH2mYyHbyII/AAAAAAAAA8M/A_o_W8By3CI/s1600/Aiza%2BSeguerra%2Band%2BLiza%2BDi%C3%B1o%2Bprenup%2Bphotos2.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;">
                <img border="0" height="314" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-8j3zPHYgwYM/VH2mYyHbyII/AAAAAAAAA8M/A_o_W8By3CI/s1600/Aiza%2BSeguerra%2Band%2BLiza%2BDi%C3%B1o%2Bprenup%2Bphotos2.jpg" width="320"/>
               </a>
              </div>
              <br/>
              <div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">
               <a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-wUpRwnVgoNM/VH2maAwOzfI/AAAAAAAAA8c/w29zCVyiWWk/s1600/Aiza%2BSeguerra%2Band%2BLiza%2BDi%C3%B1o%2Bprenup%2Bphotos3.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;">
                <img border="0" height="211" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-wUpRwnVgoNM/VH2maAwOzfI/AAAAAAAAA8c/w29zCVyiWWk/s1600/Aiza%2BSeguerra%2Band%2BLiza%2BDi%C3%B1o%2Bprenup%2Bphotos3.jpg" width="320"/>
               </a>
              </div>
              <br/>
              <div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">
               <a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-_BHTBnr6vKo/VH2mY3B2NQI/AAAAAAAAA8Q/BLjGz3Rv__A/s1600/Aiza%2BSeguerra%2Band%2BLiza%2BDi%C3%B1o%2Bprenup%2Bphotos.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;">
                <img border="0" height="242" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-_BHTBnr6vKo/VH2mY3B2NQI/AAAAAAAAA8Q/BLjGz3Rv__A/s1600/Aiza%2BSeguerra%2Band%2BLiza%2BDi%C3%B1o%2Bprenup%2Bphotos.jpg" width="320"/>
               </a>
              </div>
              <br/>
              The said photos were taken by Jason Magbanua, their official photographer. Courtesy of Liza Dio.
             </div>
             <div style="text-align: justify;">
              <br/>
             </div>
             <div style="text-align: justify;">
              In one the photos uploaded on Aizas Instagram account, the 31-year-old singer actress said that the pre-wedding shoot was The most laid-back pre-nup! (s)he experienced. Aiza said that they wanted to have the shoot relaxed and with fun just US.
             </div>
             <div style="text-align: justify;">
              <br/>
             </div>
             <div style="text-align: justify;">
              "
              <i>
               The most comfy pre-nup!!! Thanks @theproudrad for the photos and @jasonmagbanua for the video! #zazaroadto4ever
              </i>
              ," the caption read.
             </div>
             <div style="text-align: justify;">
              <br/>
             </div>
             <div style="text-align: justify;">
              Meanwhile, Dio expressed that she has already moved on from her past relationship where she had her child named Liza. Nevertheless, Seguerra still unconditionally loved Dio whatever past she may have. Aiza even firmly said that she considered Dios child as hers and willing to stand as padre de pamilya for now she claimed her own family.
             </div>
             <div style="text-align: justify;">
              <br/>
             </div>
             <div style="text-align: justify;">
              The Aiza and Liza got engaged last February this year and the couple planned to tie the knot this December 8 in the United States might as well celebrate back in the Philippines.
             </div>
